name: PortSaintLucieGuide
0:
”Alexa, ask Port Saint Lucie Guide for an attraction.”
”Give me the top five”
”tell me some facts about Port Saint Lucie.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: port saint lucie guide
des: The Port Saint Lucie Guide can be used to get an overview of the city, the attractions, and the top five things to do. If you say "open number 3" it will open number three on the top five list of things to do, same thing applies for any number up to and including five.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
